Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an8}Caramel Waffles with\N Apples and Nuts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your caramel\Nwaffles with apples and nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I've always\Nwanted to try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy! This is\Namazing! Hey, where...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...do you think I should start?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First I was an extra...\Nnow I'm a substitute, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That's all she wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is baking sweets your\Nhobby or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... I don't make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's such an amazing musician, but\Nall she looks like now is an ordinary girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I thought it was just a prop,\N but you can really play it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That piano... is such a happy piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That piano's grinning\Nfrom ear to ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sad little piano, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should never put a piano near water,\Nbut they've decorated it with fresh flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I learned it in piano class!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Megu-chan, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's Mozart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I learned this the other day.\NBut I still can't play it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Well, it\Nis pretty hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Onee-chan, can you play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She sure knows how to get along with\Nkids. I guess her mental age is low?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that Onii-chan over there\N is an unbelievable pianist,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't we ask him to teach us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me how!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I... I don't\Nplay piano anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't embarrass me in\Nfront of those children!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... just a little, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, what did I tell you?\NIt's a happy piano, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why are you stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I'm really... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am one satisfied girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You like cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used to have a black\Ncat just like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not gonna\Nplay the piano anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Winner of the Moriwaki\NStudents' Piano Competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The youngest winner in history\Nof the Saiki Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your playing style was accurate and\Ndisciplined - a human metronome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were a prodigy who performed\Nwith an orchestra at eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've done your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's common knowledge. There isn't a musician\Nof our generation who hasn't heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're who we look up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you quit playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear the\Nsound of the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How cliché is that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you were just playing\Nat that café, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I can hear it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... somewhere along the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The more I concentrate... the more I\Nget consumed by my performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds I play...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fade away from my reach, tangling up like\Nflowers seized by the spring wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't affect me at all in my daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only the sound of my\Nown playing that I can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can hear the sounds\Nof my fingers striking the keys,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the sounds of the keys sinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the only thing I can't hear is\Nthe sound of my own playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be... a punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so negative! Play\Neven if you can't play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you tried playing with a stick\Nbetween your teeth, like Beethoven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't move your hands,\Nthen play with your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have enough fingers,\Nthen use your nose as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mozart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you're sad,\Nyou're a mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or you've hit rock bottom,\Nyou still have to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how people\Nlike us survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People like us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe\Nthat's true for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since you're in love with her,\Nshe sparkles in your eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I'm with you, what Watari said\N kind of makes sense to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're in love with food,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you're in love with the violin,\Nyou're in love with music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess that's why you sparkle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you call this kind of\Nfeeling again? This is probably...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is probably what\Nyou call yearning, I bet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appointing you\Nas my accompanist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I won the Audience Award,\N I'll be playing in the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My accompanist for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you hear a word I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play, all right? I\Ncan't hear what I'm playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your whining. My mind's made up.\NJust give in to your fate like a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You exist inside spring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You exist inside a spring\Nthat can't be replaced.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby appoint Friend\NA as my accompanist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said I just can't\Ndo it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and be my accompanist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ambushing me at this hour!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For our set piece,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I decided on Saint-Saëns's\NIntroduction and Rondo Capriccioso,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I'll bring you the\Nsheet music tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.73,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Home Economics Room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have Kousei play the\Naccompaniment for your violin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got dumped by my\Naccompanist from the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's insanely\Ngood on the piano, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about that, Kao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to anyone who plays\Nmusic, he's a total celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought I'd ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think... he'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally psyched!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I just feel a chill?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I could eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they always played pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saint-Saëns's Introduction\Nand Rondo Capriccioso?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that, but it's on repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:39.52,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki\N\N\NKaori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:39.52,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accompaniment, accompaniment,\Naccompaniment, accompaniment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, open up your\Ntextbooks to page 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's you, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did she do this?\NEven my wallpaper's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play the accompaniment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.05,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play the accompaniment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Classical again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've been playing this\Nsame song for a week now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll be nice out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way he's been acting,\NKousei will bail for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna drag him\Nthere no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure it's really okay?\NTo force him to accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine. With Kousei,\Nyou have to be at least this pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good idea!\NA good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm gonna make Watari\Nhelp, too. If it's for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for you, Kao-chan,\Nno way will he say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so going to make\Nyou play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really like Arima-kun,\Ndon't you, Tsubaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite like that. To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm an only child, it's like\Nhaving a high-maintenance big sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a hopeless kid brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it doesn't matter to me\Nwhether Kousei plays the piano or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he's gonna quit, I want him to quit on\Nhis own terms. It hurts to see him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because right now, Kousei's\Nonly living his life halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, Kousei's\Nbeen trapped with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time just stops, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I want him to play the piano... Because\NI'm sure something will change if he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital Entrance...\NTotsuhara University Hospital Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:15:00.47,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Requested
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be making the next stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now commence judging the second\Nround of preliminaries for the Violin Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs14}Towa Music Competition Committee Sponsor\NSecond Annual Towa Music Competition\NViolin - Middle School Division
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs14}Towa Music Competition Committee Sponsor\NSecond Annual Towa Music Competition\NViolin - Middle School Division
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...are you doing at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the day of the prelims?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding out in a place like this! I\Nlooked all over for you, so let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been telling you all this\Ntime, I'm not gonna accompany you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there are people who train to\Nspecialize in that. No way could I ever do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, even if we\Nheaded over right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't give a performance\Nthat I could live with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, I'm casting\Nabout for a reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you can't play. You just won't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't hear the sound of the piano..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just using that as\Nyour excuse to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm at the bottom of a\Ndark sea where I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So dark... So dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you relieved the moment\Nyou stopped being able to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You found yourself an excuse. An excuse\Nnot to ever appear onstage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're no Beethoven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did his mind just go blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did he forget how to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen this happen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima's self-destructed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's one less competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...help...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the frontrunner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He cracked under the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to be alone again\Nat the bottom of a dark sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that can't hear the sound of your\Nplaying, and that you haven't been playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything. But I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you said, we might not be able to\Nturn in a performance that we can live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we're going to play. As\Nlong as I have a chance to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and there's an audience that will listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to play\Nwith everything I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that the people who've\Nheard me will never forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can live in\Ntheir hearts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my reason for existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a musician, after all! Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'm asking you to do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my accompanist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A tiny bit will do... Please\Ngive me your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please support me in this moment\Nthat I'm about to lose heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari was totally right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether or not it's impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl will let you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it. I'll be your accompanist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not making any\Nguarantees, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? We've\Nbeen looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare run away!\NNot if you call yourself a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we make a run for it,\Nwe'll be there in 20 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20 minutes? I won't be\Nable to play decently!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But will you be okay? What about\Npractice? Have you rehearsed together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! We'll figure it out!\NBecause we rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us jocks!\NI can make you time to rehearse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, shouldn't you guys be in\Nschool? And whose bike is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't sweat the small stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The town that I live in...\Nis starting to take on color...{\i0}
